com.chdryra.android.remoteapifetchers

Class FetcherGooglePlacesAPI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chdryra.android.remoteapifetchers.FetcherGooglePlacesAPI
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FetcherAutoComplete, FetcherNearbySearch, FetcherTextSearch 

    abstract class FetcherGooglePlacesAPI
extends java.lang.Object
    Fetches results for queries on Google Places API. Exactly which type of query is carried out depends on the implementation of getUrlString() by a subclass.

    Access this API through FetcherPlacesAPI static methods.

    See Also:
    FetcherPlacesAPI, Google Places API
